    "title": "Process Engineer Vacancy at Wavin India Holdings Services - 2026 Batch",
    "description": "We at Wavin India Holdings Services are looking for an experienced Process Engineer based out of Pune. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Wavin India Holdings Services:\nWavin India Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Train and supervise shop floor workers and supervisors\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Implement 5S, Kaizen, and Six Sigma practices on the shop floor\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Prepare production cost analysis and efficiency reports\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in FMEA\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n• Proficiency in TPM\n• Proficiency in 5S\n• Proficiency in PPAP\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Flexible working hours\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Wavin India Holdings Services!",
